                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.52/7–2247: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stuart</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-07-29T18:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 29, 1947—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>934. You are authorized to proceed along lines suggested Urtel 1563, July 22
                    (repeated to Shanghai as 636). Believe 6 months from date of issuance of
                    notification (sent Nanking as 934 repeated Shanghai as 1255) would be minimum
                    period acceptable for a deadline.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Marshall</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
